data.description: Step into luxury and convenience with this exquisite smart home nestled in a serene gated community.  Experience the epitome of modern living with automated lights, ceiling fans, door locks, garage door and even a smart water valve, seamlessly enhancing your daily life.  The open concept design floods the space with natural light, complimented by energy-efficient tinted windows that embrace the outdoors while maintaining privacy.  Efficiency meets elegance with spray-foam insulation and a de-humidifying A/C unit, ensuring a comfortable environment year round.  Indulge in culinary delights in the custom-designed kitchen, boasting elegant granite countertops and custom cabinetry.  Relax in the lap of luxury in the marble jetted tub, a perfect retreat in the spa-like bathrooms.  With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a formal dining room and a generously sized bonus room, this home is a haven for both relaxing and entertaining.  Loads of storage everywhere, from the closets to the oversized garage and laundry room. Enjoy the tranquility of a hidden gem that is tucked away in a gated community, yet revel in the convenience of being within walking distance of Target and Walmart.  This rare find seamlessly blends elegance, technology, and comfort.  Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your own!
